OL,3,CDogs and horses could be allowed on
OL,4,Cpopular beach for summer
OL,6,FDogs and horses could be allowed on
OL,7,FAlderney's Longis Beach this summer if
OL,8,Fpoliticians agree to a trial.
OL,10,FThe States will consider changing the
OL,11,Flaw to let them visit all year round,
OL,12,Fwith some restrictions, under a pilot
OL,13,Fscheme until the end of 2027.
OL,15,FCurrently, the animals are blocked
OL,16,Ffrom accessing it between 1 June and
OL,17,F15 September.
OL,19,FA survey completed by 640 people found
OL,20,Fthat the majority do not support an
OL,21,Fall-out ban.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G1/4
