OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779127867
OL,3,CDogs and horses could be allowed on
OL,4,Cpopular beach for summer
OL,6,FInstead, most would like dogs and
OL,7,Fhorses to be let on the beach outside
OL,8,Fof peak hours from 5pm to 8am.
OL,10,FLongis Beach is seen as the preferred
OL,11,Fspace for the trial, with survey
OL,12,Frespondents also highlighting that
OL,13,Fowners should use leads where needed,
OL,14,Fkeep animals under control and
OL,15,Fmaintain a clean and safe environment.
OL,17,FKey concerns included dog and horse
OL,18,Fmess not being picked up and the
OL,19,Fsafety of children.
OL,1,W~+$z5~{4~k4~k4~sj5  hws         G2/4
