OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F381A1779127867
OL,3,CDogs and horses could be allowed on
OL,4,Cpopular beach for summer
OL,6,FIn a statement, the States of Alderney
OL,7,Fsaid: "The proposed trial would allow
OL,8,Fthe States to assess how a managed
OL,9,Fchange could operate in practice,
OL,10,Fwhile balancing the needs of different
OL,11,Fbeach users and protecting the
OL,12,Fisland's environment."
OL,14,FMore details will follow the States
OL,15,FMeeting on Friday 29 May.
